{"tid":286470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係日本間民宿度撞鬼","createTime":"2017-06-16T15:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T13:06:48.000Z","uid":21837,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"220051a14c709608580e4c6795b673d3f7f9573a","tid":286470,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"今次係我第一次自己去日本旅行<br />\n岩岩沖完涼就拎左罐係便利店買嘅啤酒出露台諗住吹下風，思考下人生咁<br />\n咁樓上個露台同我呢個單位嘅露台都係向住同一方向突出唻<br />\n我吹緊風發緊呆之際，突然聽到樓上個露台有啲怪聲，咁我好奇心起，就伸個頭出露台向上面望<br />\n<br />\n點知就瀨野喇...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一伸個頭出去向上面望，就見到樓上個露台有個披頭散髮 臉色蒼白嘅女人，一樣烏左個身出唻向下望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同佢四目交投，佢仲E起排牙對住我笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0696f731092477d65f4776f0fcf4cd2cdf4e99e9","tid":286470,"uid":120070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"唔信，補圖"},{"pid":"772b8e45c3c582084a754eb7a8f35c2b7d6f39a2","tid":286470,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"人地未化妝姐"},{"pid":"b54a6c35387218023d74c6e48e660dd4ec8af7cd","tid":286470,"uid":106858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"大叫老子甚麼鬼也不怕!"},{"pid":"5c3a880363a5c35c0addd249f00647f32536b721","tid":286470,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"上去問下價囉"},{"pid":"ff95248ca10ea6116bd600a1a744ed8b3e27053a","tid":286470,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"a6f238bb24f152e273909d75f72650b3fe474854","tid":286470,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"其實都好呀 有人陪 唔洗毒撚自己一個人